An admin Logs In using their admin specific email address, e.g. example@admin.com
The AdminController checks if the credentials are valid for an admin log in.
AuthAdmin class calls User.getUserById(id) method, and passes is thE
users email address. If the id matches the email, the user is successfully
logged into the site. THe admin can now update a product via the addProductSubmit()
and addProductForm() methods.
